OL,3,CHow Rachel Reeves may have found #25bn
OL,4,Cbehind the back of the sofa
OL,6,FIt means public money put into
OL,7,Fdemonstratively productive investment
OL,8,F- such as wind farms, transport,
OL,9,Fgrants to businesses and so on - won't
OL,10,Fbe included in the fiscal rules' five-
OL,11,Fyear debt target.
OL,13,FI know this sounds tediously
OL,14,Ftechnical, but it has a significant
OL,15,Feconomic effect.
