OL,3,CHow Rachel Reeves may have found #25bn
OL,4,Cbehind the back of the sofa
OL,6,FIt could create #20 billion to #25
OL,7,Fbillion of "headroom" for the kind of
OL,8,Finvestment that will remain on the
OL,9,Fpublic sector balance sheet, such as
OL,10,Fin new hospitals, schools and assorted
OL,11,Fpublic-service AI and tech projects.
OL,13,FSo the freed-up billions would help
OL,14,Fmodernise and reform public services.
